# NPM: data + index.js/index.d.ts only; no Python (PyPI has porto_data/__init__.py).
# Note: "files" in package.json is the real whitelist; entries in "files" are always
# included and .npmignore cannot exclude them. Do NOT add "porto_data" as a whole
# to "files" — only porto_data/data, porto_data/schemas, porto_data/*.json.
*.py
*.pyc
porto_data/__init__.py
porto_data/py.typed
**/__pycache__/
*.pyi
pyproject.toml
scripts/
cli/
tests/
.cursorrules
